Enemy Containers implemented
- Added a state machine with 4 states: - - Spawning - - Moving - - Defeated - - Despawning For now, only Spawning and Moving, with a transition between two have been implemented - Logic controlling enemy movement along path moved to enemy class itself - Commented out code in Map relating to logic until fully fleshed out and 100% working

Enemy Containers created
- Created EnemyContainer parent scene - Created two inherited scenes for: Scumbug and Snail - Commented out old curve3D pathfinding curve for now - Starting work on state machines next

Overhaul of wave system
- Added autoload of path_generator.gd script to be accessible as PathGenInstance - Created path_generator_config that extends Resoruce to enable saving/changing of level variables much easier - Created resources to store data for our easy/medium/map extending above new config - Added few comments of some functions to allow better understanding - Complete overhaul of previous map_parent and path_generator code to better suit new system
